{"tid":708800,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"甄子丹扮拿破崙騎戰馬","createTime":"2018-06-19T14:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T06:37:54.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f17951c273c09c29fbdb27583672a5c5edf80afe","tid":708800,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"甄子丹和超模杜鵑日前遠赴英國，為新濠天地拍攝全新品牌概念照，照片由國際頂尖攝影師Nick Knight操刀，他曾為英女皇伊利沙伯二世及英國皇儲查理斯拍攝紀念照。子丹的造型啟發自19世紀法國皇帝拿破崙策騎白色戰馬，相中的子丹威風凜凜，散發王者權威，他說︰「雖然自己本身擅於策騎，但要表現拿破崙莊嚴雄偉的一面，又要令白馬展現箇中美態，整個拍攝項目實在令人難忘。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2095236/20180615JLC006__20180615_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2095236%2F20180615JLC006__20180615_L.jpg&h=a571e2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n丹爺係咪中伏？扮矮仔拿破崙"},{"pid":"6c8ba74ea4f601cdc442847f98b40e180b77d80b","tid":708800,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"雖然佢本身出身書香世家 父母一文一武 自己又外國長大 又鬼仔格又見識多 自己又能文能武 但近呢幾年開始個款唔止係明星同愈來愈紅 依家係直頭開始似啲名門權貴咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a132c68188cc3a744dd4cc1feb504b665e3c64b","tid":708800,"uid":105445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/120947_3207f19e80a93c0a8b1f395971d74b8a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F120947_3207f19e80a93c0a8b1f395971d74b8a.gif&h=b06f66ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你邊個on鳩仔扮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2deb9788fe209e19cc7a1dac9d1a38fcf8591b10","tid":708800,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯佢扮隻馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ace46e0c14e